HEADWORD: Contraindication
<hw>Con"tra*in`di*ca"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<fld>(med.)</fld> <def>An indication or symptom which forbids the method
of treatment usual in such cases.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

